headline: Philip Morris Stock Is Hot. A Lot of Credit Goes to Zyn.
summary: One of the successor companies of the old maker of Marlboro cigarettes has gone big in smokeless as smoking has declined globally, most recently with a nicotine pouch from Sweden called Zyn.
